H-0086.5 _______________________________________________ HOUSE BILL 1294 _______________________________________________ State of Washington 56th Legislature 1999 Regular Session By Representatives Fisher and K. Schmidt Read first time 01/21/1999.
Referred to Committee on Transportation.
